genresAdvancedInfo.name: malayalam worship
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Malayalam worship music is a genre of Christian music that is popular in Kerala, India. It features devotional lyrics in Malayalam and is usually performed in churches or during religious gatherings. The music is often slow and contemplative, with a focus on praising God and expressing gratitude.
